# Stage 03 — wave_planner (L2)

Runs the deterministic wave-planner on top of the `plan.md` from stage 02 design. Builds a DAG from explicit dependencies and file footprints, partitions tasks into topological waves respecting the subagent cap per tier (2/3/5/5), and writes `wave-plan.md` with the list of branches to create for stage 04. This stage is deterministic: cycles in the plan become `BLOCKED_ERROR`, not a stop point.

